description:
On Today's episode of the Dan Patrick show DP recaps last night's Quarterbacks duel between Cam Newton and Joe Flacco. The Jets remain winless, would you avoid New York if you were Trevor Lawrence? We're joined by sportscaster, Jim Gray and ESPN Senior Writer/ Author of "Pappyland", Wright Thompson. Plus, they guys discuss which sounds should be pumped into the Masters broadcast.
